{"tid":142691,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"和黃旗下藥廠 研發腸癌新藥獲重大進展","createTime":"2017-03-04T03:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T10:31:28.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6f95644be7e08bbaad5605fd91d0709dc3519f","tid":142691,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"和黃旗下藥廠<br />\n研發腸癌新藥獲重大進展<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】李嘉誠旗下和黃中國醫藥科技，昨日公佈公司一直研發結直腸癌新藥，在後期研製階段，獲得重大進展。消息刺激這間在英國倫敦上市的公司，股價急升近10%，截至晚上10時半止，報22.875英鎊。長和（001）持有和黃中國醫藥科技60.4%股份。<br />\n和黃中國醫藥稱，新藥的3期關鍵註冊臨床試驗成功，416名參加新藥試驗的患者，均是接受兩輪化療失敗的轉移性結腸癌病人。他們接受新藥後，整體生存時間顯著延長，並達到了具有統計學及臨床的意義，正準備向中國食品藥品監督管理局，提交新藥上市申請。<br />\n公司董事長杜志強在新聞稿內稱，經過10多年努力及巨大的投入，新藥在臨床試驗中成功，不僅是病人福音，亦是公司重大里程碑。他估計新藥向監管當局申請，預計在今年中完成。"},{"pid":"fa45147a76e459a9ddaf177049a8459f5f7ca741","tid":142691,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"誠哥已經長生不老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065621a1934ce3d45892629fce913663a08751b8","tid":142691,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"有關人士已經係消息出嚟前入滿貨，早段會邊拉高邊引老散追入派貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872b6e0fcbb0225b433fb42121add34874313f92","tid":142691,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"一陣睇下d 報告先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2aadd84a61b52d50c846c17ab83a0e6ee75782","tid":142691,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"中國人做假是常識吧"},{"pid":"b1d40b9f86e6fd53768db2e64094be9baa00850e","tid":142691,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"好快會比人暗殺"},{"pid":"7576ac8f669b7a3e9bd2fac3851babeb3a422513","tid":142691,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好快會比人暗殺</blockquote><br />\n藥廠自己研發呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfe0fe26632a081fe1a9cbf17e826f3ea6ff156","tid":142691,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"股市活躍，細價股，毫子股「利好消息」層出不窮定律"},{"pid":"5d623d72de1fb3ca19305de0b000d91f4c2eec48","tid":142691,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:35:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa0a697ef4642ea9cfb20aee48af5d14ce897441","tid":142691,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:35:39.000Z","msg":"加油 供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75602b88730821650b6dfe51a1989916c5214a0","tid":142691,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"1號升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}